## Series Promotion Strategy

### Before the Series Launches

- [ ] Announce the series 1 week before Piece 1 publishes
- [ ] Create a series landing page or thread that will link to all pieces
- [ ] Tease the topic on social platforms to gauge interest
- [ ] Email list: send a preview or "coming soon" mention

### During the Series

- [ ] Each piece links back to previous pieces and forward to the series landing page
- [ ] Cross-promote each piece on secondary platforms within 24 hours of publication
- [ ] Engage with comments and feedback to build discussion around the series
- [ ] Mid-series check-in: share what you have learned so far, tease what is coming

### After the Series Completes

- [ ] Publish a summary/recap piece that synthesizes the entire series
- [ ] Create a compilation (e.g., "The Complete Guide to [Topic]")
- [ ] Share the full series as a resource in relevant communities
- [ ] Evaluate performance and decide whether to extend or spin off a related series

